Just please make sure that you always start each mainImage with fragColor=vec4(0) to avoid unintentional uninitialized output value. (function's out parameters must be properly initialized)
For example in buffers B, C and D you exit early if FORCED_RATIO is defined so fragColor is never set.
Because of that on Mac mini there are some horizontal lines with noise near top and bottom of the image.
